                </h2>

                <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-base-content/90 leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        I'm a <strong class="text-primary">Systems Engineer</strong> from Colombia, with over
                        <strong class="text-primary">10 years</strong> of experience building digital products that solve
                        real-world problems. Currently pursuing a <strong class="text-primary">Master's in Computer Engineering</strong>
                        while working as a <strong class="text-primary">CTO and technology consultant</strong> for startups and enterprises.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        My journey in software development started with a simple philosophy:
                        <em class="text-secondary font-semibold">"Create simple solutions to complex problems."</em>
                        This approach has guided me through building everything from mobile banking applications serving
                        thousands of users to blockchain-powered digital wallets handling tens of thousands of daily transactions.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        As <strong class="text-primary">Co-founder & CTO of Monetta Project</strong>, I led a team of 10 engineers
                        to build a cross-platform digital wallet with blockchain integration on Polygon network. This experience
                        taught me not just about technology, but about leadership, team dynamics, and the importance of balancing
                        technical excellence with business objectives.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Throughout my career, I've had the privilege of working with <strong class="text-primary">Colombia's
                        largest financial institutions</strong>, building geolocation systems, mobile banking platforms, and
                        payment solutions that impact hundreds of thousands of users daily.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- What I Do - Grid -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-base-content mb-8 text-center">What I Do</h2>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 to-blue-600/10 border-2 border-blue-500/20 hover:border-blue-500/40 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üöÄ</div>
                        <h3 class="card-title text-base-content">Technical Leadership</h3>
                        <p class="text-base-content/80">
                            Leading engineering teams, defining architecture, and establishing best practices
