                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title text-2xl text-base-content mb-4">Beyond Code</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-base-content/90 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        When I'm not building software, I'm usually exploring new technologies through side projects,
                        contributing to open-source, or learning about emerging trends in software architecture and
                        system design. I'm particularly interested in the intersection of blockchain technology and
                        traditional financial services.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-base-content/90 leading-relaxed">
                        I'm based in <strong class="text-primary">Granada, Spain</strong>, and I'm
